        <caption>
          <p><bold>Overview of KVFinder GUI.</bold> Example of KVFinder’s graphical user interface. The search space delimitation is made through a customizable box. In the example, it was defined around the ligand of the [PBB: 2J6L].</p>
        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="1471-2105-15-197-2"/>
