        <caption>
          <p><bold>KVFinder results on the GUI.</bold> Example of results being displayed on the graphical interface. Here a whole protein prospection was made on the target protein structure [PDB:1FW1], and information of every cavity is displayed. To aid cavity identification, a highlight tool is available through selection. We can also see interactively the forming residues of each cavity.</p>
        </caption>
